then starts wailing.

12:32.217 --> 12:34.285
Look, I know you got
a lot on your plate,

12:34.286 --> 12:36.254
with New York and planning
our wedding and whatnot,

12:36.255 --> 12:38.172
but you're at your best
when you're under pressure.

12:38.173 --> 12:40.291
Now, turn around
and show us

12:40.292 --> 12:41.843
